 to some of the deepest questions one’s life. This distinguished translation brings Földényi’s work directly to English-language readers for the first time.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 24. Mai 2022) 0aDepression, Mental. 0aMelancholy. 7aLITERARY CRITICISM / European / General.2bisacsh1 aManguel, Alberto, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aManguel, Alberto.1 aWilkinson, Tim.08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertYale University Press Complete eBook-Package 2016z978311066771440uhttps://doi.org/10.12987/978030022069840uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9780300220698423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9780300220698/original  a978-3-11-066771-4  Yale University Press Complete eBook-Package 2016b2016  aEBA_FAO  aEBA_UCA_YUP  aGBV-deGruyter-alles